{"tid":701082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街親戚","createTime":"2018-06-14T00:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T03:03:16.000Z","uid":130466,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ecf9e89702b32b191836f0046081e1b147fb8e","tid":701082,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T00:34:35.000Z","msg":"唔係facebook 有當年今日，我都唔會記得呢件事。 如下文：<br />\n<br />\n每個人身邊都一定有那麼一個壞親戚,細個果陣有個親戚見我帶眼鏡就話:[帶眼鏡丫,第日大個實做掃街啦!] 結果,佢依家一把年紀俾我見到佢係賭場到做清潔工人,倒垃圾、擦窗、拖地咩都要做。真係要對佢講句,一把年紀仲咁肯捱,抵你冚家富貴啦!!<br />\n<br />\n有點咁既親戚真係仆街，細細個邊個唔係好純純到成舊雞咁，班廢老就要係d令仔身上面搵成就感，真係可悲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c372bb338bb6c266ad1571923174516dd04ed653","tid":701082,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T00:42:49.000Z","msg":"戴眼鏡同掃街有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8f2b2802fe2114d01d12eb380681fb5f73391e","tid":701082,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c372bb338bb6c266ad1571923174516dd04ed653","tid":701082,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T00:42:49.000Z","msg":"戴眼鏡同掃街有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"純粹想串鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}